# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# AEGIS is a TAURI APP. See ARCHITECTURE.md.
# These ignores prevent v2 Node.js daemon artifacts from returning.
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# === V2 ARTIFACTS — THESE DO NOT BELONG IN THIS REPO ===
# If you see these directories, read ARCHITECTURE.md immediately.
/src/
assets/
scripts/
installer/
dist/
release/
build-release.mjs
AEGIS-silent.vbs
AEGIS.cmd
AEGIS-Setup-*.exe
VERSION
.npmrc
_*.py
_*.txt
_*.cjs
git-*.txt
lint-*.txt
tsc-*.txt

# === STANDARD IGNORES ===
node_modules/
*.exe
!src-tauri/binaries/*.exe
*.log
.env
state.json
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.js.map

# === SIDECAR BUILD OUTPUT ===
sidecar/dist/

# === RUST BUILD OUTPUT ===
src-tauri/target/

# === TRANSIENT ===
commit-msg.txt
# MORNING_BRIEFING.md is tracked — included in commits per session-close spec
